{
  "stem": "7016.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 20.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In-- in-- it was a special place, where we'd buried.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the-- and this was the job what we have to do every time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I probably was 20, 21.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is why I said it's so painful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's so painful to tell this everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And beside this, I said, if I wouldn't be there, if somebody would tell me those stories, I wouldn't believe it either.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's hard to believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's very hard to believe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just, you know, every day you saw people dying, dying, dying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not many left in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The only thing was you don't-- you-- you was not so afraid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know you're going to die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But you're not afraid the-- the selections, and the Mengele.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And those-- and those-- to go through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "From this you didn't have-- you wasn't [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, uh, I think this-- this was the life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We went through every day the same thing, the same thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I got a friends there, what she was so close to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She helped me a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We was working together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was still-- didn't feel good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was spitting with blood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then, one time they start to talk, we saw airplanes running.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That maybe they come and they put some bombs here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We all got killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Not to suffer so much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And, uh, one time it-- they came-- this was the end, I think, of the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It-- it came the end-- the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We was in the barracks, and it came out with trucks, the-- the-- the Army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We was thinking this is the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They're going to take us away.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
